track_notes: After Low Fell track takes you to the Wainwright of Fellbarrow (LDW-199). Roadside parking available for several cars north of Brook Farm.

This route is from the Car Park nr Loweswater Hall, along the road then cuts the corner in to wood. (The zig Zags are poor GPS coverage) then up the track to a gate. Turn right onto the fell and follow round. At the fence there is a steep up hill to the ridge. Go over the fence and along the ridge to the summit.
